Start Point: Find the book "Soul Journey" in the College Library.

Official Difficulty: Intermediate

Description: A book in the College of Winterhold claims to have the location of an artifact that can passively fill soul gems for you. Find it and retrieve it.

Official length: Short

Requirements: None

Items required: A weapon

Enemies to defeat: Several Vampires

Quest Stages: 

0 - I read a book that told me of an artifact that fills up souls gem, using septims as energy.
10 - I have spoken to Urag gro-Shrub, who believes that the artifact was last seen in Haemar's Shame.
200 - I have retrieved the artefact.

Rewards: Soul Bearer (Fills soul gems passively, 10 septims per charge)
